data.description: Gorgeous home with charming backyard oasis, swimming pool, and direct access to 75 miles of Greenbelt trails. The backyard is tranquil for relaxation and an inviting atmosphere for fun and entertainment with family and friends. Boasting large, picturesque windows which showcase a spectacular view from the kitchen and breakfast area. Enjoy time outside under the extended covered patio. This well-maintained home has so much to offer with lots of natural light, spacious rooms, and situated in the affluent neighborhood of Kingwood.  This luxurious property is a dream home with a fantastic location! Nearby local amenities such as H-E-B grocery store, a variety of shopping and restaurants, florist, Kingwood Country Club, access to Metro public transportation, the community center, Public Library, Sand Creek Village neighborhood pool and park, and Humble I.S.D schools. This dream home has NO back neighbors, NO history of flooding and is move-in ready!  Refrigerator included.
